{"tid":1717802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【保密身份大整合】唔好做燒山，靜靜地贏.gif","createTime":"2019-11-13T16:43:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T16:53:41.000Z","uid":202895,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af8c8a6e4691125f8eb24ba6cd64184a765ea8c8","tid":1717802,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">古語有云：「沉默是金」</div></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 鏡頭前戴返個口罩（<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>尤其是食野飲水個陣，一係開遮擋住食啦，一係一睇到就上返口罩</strong></span>）<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔好係CCTV下同他人眼光下換裝（<strong><ins>哨兵眼前</ins></strong>都係）<br />\n<br />\n3. 唔好係<strong><ins>任何地方同任何人</ins></strong>透露發夢細節，包括上<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>家長車</strong></span>個陣都係<br />\n<br />\n4. 唔好打卡，唔好Post手足動靜（包括新發明）<br />\n<br />\n5. 唔好對記者咁友好，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保持警惕</strong></span></strong>（慎防紅媒）【知唔知道最親近人類嘅流浪貓狗係最危險，同理】<br />\n<br />\n6. 留意有冇人跟蹤，參考多個反跟蹤方法，例如行快後突然急停等等&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n7. 唔好係被D奇怪嘅人R你傾計個陣，同佢講<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任何野</span></strong>，請無視佢，仲有提下隔離手足<br />\n<br />\n8. 大戰時不透露大隊行蹤比記者，不被鏡頭聽到討論結果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人最希望大家留意係第5點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝大家靜靜地贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e223b25b9e5b2e6e999bd0986750867ece47de","tid":1717802,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7e49d60eafb16e32e199a83d301eb532faffed","tid":1717802,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44419f71d2374a94b0ceb96db601e5bfdb317a9c","tid":1717802,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b920b2c3eb5a8030e2c816fe6a549646364eed6f","tid":1717802,"uid":202895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:47:40.000Z","msg":"知唔知TVB都轉咗玩法<br />\n係買人地嘅影片再自己CUT頭CUT尾<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再對記者咁過度友好啦，比返d警惕黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092b0d8a710a65f0350fcdd3e42e1b2a8bf53323","tid":1717802,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c433c7e4f5e1f0f0dfaf22e8236a05700dadd63","tid":1717802,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6425b6ba8d3de87be1585054941c27b3c74e33af","tid":1717802,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c547c02e85942f42d3ffb4b47fe6882110fbe0db","tid":1717802,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}